Hi Everyone,

ABPNI Computer Solutions Ltd, the proud owners of Evorack, is pleased to launch a new brand: Rackburst.

The concept of Rackburst is simple: Quality, Low-Cost, UK OpenVZ VPS using SuperFast SSD RAID10 disk storage and enterprise-class 

Intel Xeon Processors. Our network is monitored 24/7 and our servers are located in the Rapidswitch datacentre in Nottingham.

Test Server: speedtest.rackburst.net (88.150.169.131)

The plans which meet the LEB/LET criteria are as follows:

**Apartment**&lt;br /&gt;
Dedicated RAM: 256MB&lt;br /&gt;
including vSwap: 512MB&lt;br /&gt;
SuperFast Storage: 3GB SSD RAID10&lt;br /&gt;
Mountable Remote Storage: 20GB&lt;br /&gt;
CPU Cores: 2&lt;br /&gt;
Bandwidth: 350GB&lt;br /&gt;
Price per month: £1.49 (yearly), £1.79 otherwise&lt;br /&gt;

**Cottage**&lt;br /&gt;
Dedicated RAM: 512MB&lt;br /&gt;
including vSwap: 1024MB&lt;br /&gt;
SuperFast Storage: 6GB SSD RAID10&lt;br /&gt;
Mountable Remote Storage: 30GB&lt;br /&gt;
CPU Cores: 4&lt;br /&gt;
Bandwidth: 550GB&lt;br /&gt;
Price per month: £2.99 (yearly), £3.29 otherwise&lt;br /&gt;

All orders (that aren't marked as fruad) are set up instantly. Customers also have full control of their VPS via the SolusVM control panel.

Support is available via our legendary Live Support service on our website, or via usual support tickets in the customer portal.

To order your VPS today, please visit [http://www.rackburst.net](http://www.rackburst.net)

If anyone has any questions, please feel free to ask.

